channel.description:

item.dc:creator: @CChhrriiss CChhrriiss
item.description:
@CChhrriiss wrote:

Go to the player files and click on your username
change the player rights to 3

Player rights code
1 - mod
2 - admin
3 - owner
4 - hidden admin/ownerafter that save it and compile your server, you’ll need to be logged out for it to work.
